.TH _PRINTF 3 "APRIL 2026" "Holberton School" "Custom Printf Manual"
.SH NAME
_printf \- formatted output conversion
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include "main.h"
.sp
.B int _printf(const char *format, ...);
.SH DESCRIPTION
The \fB_printf\fP() function produces output according to a \fIformat\fP.
It writes output to \fBstdout\fP, the standard output stream.
